Har Kadane question se pehle sirf ye 5 questions pucho:

1. Main optimize kya kar raha hu?
   (sum/product/profit/etc)

2. Kya current segment continue karna beneficial hai?

3. Kya current segment discard karna beneficial hai?

4. Har index pe meri state kya hai?
   (currSum, currProduct, etc)

5. Global answer kaise update hoga?


